	<title>View menu </title>
	<media type="image" mime="image/png" width="187" height="165" src="./Manual/Viewmenu.png"/>

	<p>These options affect how the puzzle is displayed.  There are no equivalent toolbar icons</p>
	<list>
		<item><p><em>Toolbar</em></p>
			<p>Selected by default.  Determines whether the toolbar is displayed.  Removing the toolbar creates a little more space for larger puzzles.</p>
		</item>
		<item><p><em>Grid</em></p>
			<p>By default, the grid is not displayed when setting a puzzle (to get a better picture effect) and displayed when solving. This option allows this behavious to be overridden</p>
		</item>

	</list>
